Description:
WHY FIT IN WHEN YOU CAN STAND OUT
"The classic line from Dr. Seuss has never been more relevant than when referring to 12 Seuss Drive."
Why fit in with all the others when you can stand out? Standing proudly in one of Officer's quirkiest estate, Arcadia, the four bedroom property is quite remarkable.
Built by one of the best builders going around, Henley Constructions, and fitted with the upgraded package, this home is less than two years old will impress. On top of this it still has 48 more years worth of Henley structural guarantee.
With Officer Secondary College only a stones throw and all local amenities only a brief commute you will not want to look further
With all the modern upgrade comes this complete home ready to go.
Showcasing:
- Master bedroom with stone benched en-suite and walk in robe;
- Open plan kitchen with 900mm stainless steel appliances, glass splashback and 20mm caesar stone bench with cascading waterfall bench tops;
- Living with laminate floorboards;
- Kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances and dishwasher, ample bench and cupboard space;
- Seperate living area;
- Two minor bedrooms also fitted with walk-in robe while the fourth has built-in robe;
- Main bathroom with bath;
- Double garage with updated grain grand garage pack and internal access;
- Alfresco;
- Landscaped gardens and garden shed for additional storage;
- NBN ready;
- Ducted heating and 2 split system airconditioners including a 7kw unit in the living room and one in the master bedroom.
Ray White prides itself on being as accurate as possible however anyone considering purchasing the property should undertake their own due diligence to confirm the above.
